Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_pkt_output_wmark

This register sets the value that determines when backpressure is applied to the PKO. When SLI_PKT()_SLIST_BAOFF_DBELL[DBELL] is less than [WMARK], backpressure is sent to PKO for the associated channel. This register is PF-only.
